<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 06:20:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台积电Q3利润大涨54% 好于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-q3-profit-rises-54-better-than-forecasts-2024-10-17/</link><description>台湾芯片制造商台积电周四公布第三季度净利润增长 54%，超出市场预期，因为该公司继续从人工智能应用中使用的半导体需求激增中获益。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 05:37:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-q3-profit-rises-54-better-than-forecasts-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国问题拖累保乐力加第一季度销售额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-woes-drag-down-pernod-ricards-q1-sales-2024-10-17/</link><description>法国烈酒制造商保乐力加表示，尽管其第一季度销售额下降了 5.9%，低于预期（部分原因是中国市场疲软），但仍预计 2024/25 财年将恢复销售增长。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 05:32:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-woes-drag-down-pernod-ricards-q1-sales-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>迅达第三季度销量因新安装量减少和中国疲软而小幅下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-third-quarter-sales-slightly-fall-lower-new-installations-2024-10-17/</link><description>瑞士电梯和自动扶梯制造商迅达周四报告称，由于新安装量下降（主要是在中国），第三季度销售额下降 0.9%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 04:44:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-third-quarter-sales-slightly-fall-lower-new-installations-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，麦肯锡中国业务裁员数百人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/mckinsey-cuts-hundreds-jobs-china-business-wsj-reports-2024-10-17/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周三报道，美国咨询公司麦肯锡在减少与政府相关的客户并裁员约 500 人（约占其中国员工总数的三分之一）后，正在重组其中国业务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 03:54:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/mckinsey-cuts-hundreds-jobs-china-business-wsj-reports-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>台湾高级官员称，中国正在建设快速打击台湾的能力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-building-capacity-rapidly-strike-taiwan-senior-taiwanese-official-says-2024-10-17/</link><description>台湾一名高级安全官员表示，中国正在建设迅速将军事演习转变为全面攻击的能力，并提供了台北政府对北京本周在台湾进行的军演背后的战略意图的评估。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 03:03:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-building-capacity-rapidly-strike-taiwan-senior-taiwanese-official-says-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>Bajaj Auto 的节日销售警告加剧印度股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-shares-set-open-slightly-higher-earnings-focus-2024-10-17/</link><description>印度股市周四下跌，原因是摩托车制造商 Bajaj Auto 对节日季销售疲软的警告波及整个行业，加剧了高股票估值和外国资金外流的压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 02:41:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indian-shares-set-open-slightly-higher-earnings-focus-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国增加住房项目资金以支持陷入困境的行业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expand-financing-housing-projects-4-trln-yuan-says-housing-minister-2024-10-17/</link><description>中国住房和城乡建设部部长倪虹周四表示，中国将扩大符合融资条件的住房项目“白名单”，并在年底前将此类开发项目的银行贷款增加至4万亿元人民币（5620亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 02:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expand-financing-housing-projects-4-trln-yuan-says-housing-minister-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因中国住房计划而停滞，“特朗普贸易”提振美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-17/</link><description>亚洲股市周四回吐早盘涨幅，原因是中国的住房政策简报令投资者失望，而美元因唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)当选总统的前景而升至2-1/2个月高点附近。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 01:54:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>日本首相石破茂在大选前向靖国神社献祭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-pm-ishiba-sends-offering-yasukuni-shrine-ahead-election-2024-10-17/</link><description>日本首相石破茂的办公室周四表示，他向东京靖国神社献上了祭品，此举引起了韩国的批评，韩国认为靖国神社是日本军国主义过去的象征。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 01:08:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-pm-ishiba-sends-offering-yasukuni-shrine-ahead-election-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>澳元因就业意外上涨；美元坚守“特朗普贸易”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-11-week-high-eyes-china-property-briefing-2024-10-17/</link><description>就业数据连续六个月超出预期后，澳元周四上涨，而美元则保持在 11 周高点附近，因特朗普在即将到来的美国大选中可能获胜而获得额外支撑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 00:41:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-11-week-high-eyes-china-property-briefing-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国称日本渔船“非法”进入领海</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-japanese-fishing-boat-illegally-entered-territorial-2024-10-17/</link><description>中国海警称，10月15日至16日，一艘日本渔船“非法进入”中国钓鱼岛领海，并被警告驱离。</description><pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 00:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-japanese-fishing-boat-illegally-entered-territorial-2024-10-17/</guid></item><item><title>禾赛重返美国涉嫌帮助北京军方的公司名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/pentagon-removes-lidar-maker-hesai-us-list-firms-alleged-help-beijings-military-2024-10-16/</link><description>根据一份法庭文件和发送给国会的两封信，美国国防部将激光雷达制造商禾赛集团从涉嫌与北京军方合作的公司名单中删除，但将立即将这家中国公司重新列入名单。</description><pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 22:21:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/pentagon-removes-lidar-maker-hesai-us-list-firms-alleged-help-beijings-military-2024-10-16/</guid></item><item><title>经合组织支持的组织呼吁制定全球协议解决水危机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/oecd-backed-group-calls-global-pact-solve-water-crisis-2024-10-16/</link><description>经合组织支持的一个委员会周四表示，各国需要一项新的国际协议来解决日益严重的水危机，到 2050 年，水危机可能会使经济增长至少下降 8%，并使世界一半的粮食供应面临风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 22:06:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/oecd-backed-group-calls-global-pact-solve-water-crisis-2024-10-16/</guid></item><item><title>台积电第三季度利润轻松超过人工智能繁荣预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-set-report-strong-profit-driven-by-ai-boom-2024-10-16/</link><description>人工智能应用先进芯片的主要生产商台积电周四公布，由于需求飙升，第三季度利润增长 54%，超出预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 22:02:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-set-report-strong-profit-driven-by-ai-boom-2024-10-16/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：通胀降温，台积电提供AI风向标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-16/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 21:49:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>